download the zip folder containing the GRID dataset using this link https://drive.google.com/file/d/187JQdiqoFGV8KKEhVP0lRwpLgdftETYJ/view?usp=drive_link
Follow the instructions in DLR/Instructions.txt
Run Reorganize_dataset_phrases_as_LRS2.py in order to adapt the structure of MIRACL-VC1 to the model
To run the test use the path of the newly MIRACL-VC1 dataset on your local machine in --data_path
python main.py --gpu_id 0 --lip_model_path deep_lip_reading/lrs2_lip_model --data_path path_to_dataset/MIRACL-VC1 --data_list media/lrs2_test_samples.txt 
